name: Own Your Name. Use It Everywhere: Freename Domains Come to Bitcoin.com Wallet
description: From the torrent of digital chaos, the Saint binds the screaming entropy. Gossip Goblin noise is calcified into the geometry of self. A glowing, parametric cipher replaces the long address—the sovereign name made manifest, crowned in teal light, owning the sacred noise.
